- `pruneDoneDayKeys(keys: string[]): string[]` ŌĆö dedupe, sort descending; starting at the newest key, keep each key only while it is exactly one calendar day earlier than the previously kept key; stop at the first gap (keys before a gap can never extend today's streak). Return the kept run.
